話無左波箱問題<br />\n同埋想知 7代1.4 tsi係咪即係gt tsi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"Gt = 1.4+turbo 好似係"},{"pid":"accef7cff8a3c13408afc86a5b80c07bd64223ba","tid":1680660,"uid":64925,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"一直要買乾式7速波箱嘅車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc4d2abe03059554e0bd841300579bcc2ecf1d8","tid":1680660,"uid":139176,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"係咪mk仔<br />\n要買golf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768378d5417352ef09780a89e3c05ae60cd59117","tid":1680660,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"想下算"},{"pid":"5bc82d326877f8170b264ca6e738392fc4261478","tid":1680660,"uid":8717,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c78680143ce05fe5fe17980840896d5acb7b0bd7","tid":1680660,"uid":126663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"維修保養煩唔煩<br />\n上網睇2013年之後既golf 話無左波箱問題<br />\n同埋想知 7代1.4 tsi係咪即係gt tsi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"12年小改後個波箱己經會耐用左<br />\n<br />\n不過無論6代,7代既TSI GT, 還是濕式既GTI 佢地既波箱電腦一樣會咁上下時間收皮, 濕式亦只係相對耐用並唔係完全無問題. 單講可靠仍然係無法同日本車比. 所以如果你買得佢地就要預呢個波箱電腦係消秏品, 大概6~8萬公里執一次就岩, 價錢算親民, 車房大概萬二蚊, 番廠就萬六蚊鬆. 其他都係一般歐洲車既電子問題唔算太多野整. <br />\n<br />\n如果阿Q D諗, 宜家一部七代六萬蚊上落都有得簡下. 咁既價錢買到咁既質素其實幾抵玩, 平左既車價當資助你整一獲."},{"pid":"1c225cda6c44e86141eeafa34039b51d2deb8ba7","tid":1680660,"uid":13908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dca5417156c685dcf74ef33af76f689d46f68095","tid":1680660,"uid":57041,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c78680143ce05fe5fe1798084089