3D&h=6fb56491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ecutesting.com/common-faults/volkswagen/volkswagen-golf-audi-a3-dsg-7-gearbox-problem/</a>"},{"pid":"0f2348cce82af8c05425b56b128d23513b1c7e94","tid":1680660,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc82d326877f8170b264ca6e738392fc4261478","tid":1680660,"uid":8717,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c78680143ce05fe5fe17980840896d5acb7b0bd7","tid":1680660,"uid":126663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"維修保養煩唔煩<br />\n上網睇2013年之後既golf 話無左波箱問題<br />\n同埋想知 7代1.4 tsi係咪即係gt tsi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"12年小改後個波箱己經會耐用左<br />\n<br />\n不過無論6代,7代既TSI GT, 還是濕式既GTI 佢地既波箱電腦一樣會咁上下時間收皮, 濕式亦只係相對耐用並唔係完全無問題. 單講可靠仍然係無法同日本車比. 所以如果你買得佢地就要預呢個波箱電腦係消秏品, 大概6~8萬公里執一次就岩, 價錢算親民, 車房大概萬二蚊, 番廠就萬六蚊鬆. 其他都係一般歐洲車既電子問題唔算太多野整. <br />\n<br />\n如果阿Q D諗, 宜家一部七代六萬蚊上落都有得簡下. 咁既價錢買到咁既質素其實幾抵玩, 平左既車價當資助你整一獲."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"我10年 9萬幾公里都十分正常"},{"pid":"66a7e16892cdf6463551db688be25949024e2b70","tid":1680660,"uid":8717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f2348cce82af8c05425b56b128d23513b1c7e94","tid":1680660,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc82d326877f8170b264ca6e738392fc4261478","tid":1680660,"uid":8717,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c78680143ce05fe5fe17980840896d5acb7b0bd7","tid":1680660,"uid":126663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"維修保養煩唔煩<br />\n上網睇2013年之後既golf 話無左波箱問題<br />\n同埋想知 7代1.4 tsi係咪即係gt tsi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"12年小改後個波箱己經會耐用左<br />\n<br />\n不過無論6代,7代既TSI GT, 還是濕式既GTI 佢地既波箱電腦一樣會咁上